info.name: 03. Pelayanan - IGD
info.description:
This folder is the result of merged folder "**13\. SATUSEHAT- Modul Pelayanan IGD Fase 1**" and "**16\. SATUSEHAT- Modul Pelayanan IGD Fase 2**". For **complete repository for all SATUSEHAT use-cases** please access our public workspaces : [Postman Workspaces](https://s.id/PostmanSATUSEHAT) For **detailed SATUSEHAT use-cases import link** please see : [Postman Public Kemkes Link](https://link.kemkes.go.id/PostmanSATUSEHAT) Any information about SATUSEHAT FHIR Profile could be accessed through [Simplifier FHIR Profile](https://simplifier.net/guide/SATUSEHAT-FHIR-R4-Implementation-Guide/Home/FHIRProfiles?version=current) Silakan **akses riwayat perubahan** pada Playbook dan pelajari API Collection (Postman). | **Folder History** | **Editor** | **Date** | | --- | --- | --- | | First Revision - Merged From Old Folders (13. SATUSEHAT - Modul Pelayanan IGD Fase 1 & 16. SATUSEHAT - Modul Pelayanan IGD Fase 2) | [luthfi.qonitah@dto.kemkes.go.id

](https://mailto:luthfi.qonitah@dto.kemkes.go.id)[sania.fitria@dto.kemkes.go.id](https://mailto:sania.fitria@dto.kemkes.go.id) | 26-04-2024 |
